title: Chancellor's big play allows Seattle to beat Detroit 13-10
text:
> Washington Chancellor's big play allows Seattle to beat Detroit 13-10 Seattle Seahawks wide receiver Doug Baldwin (89) is greeted by wide receiver Tyler Lockett, right, after Baldwin scored a touchdown in the first half of an NFL football game against the Detroit Lions, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015, in Seattle. (AP Photo/Elaine Thompson)
